"{\"uid\": \"nytimes.com-athletic-5303256-2024-02-27-uswnt-mexico-olympics-nwsl-kits\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"NWSL      Lots going on.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 24, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Let us get right into it.\", \"from\": 25, \"to\": 50, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I amEmily Olsenhere withMeg LinehanandSteph Yang- welcome to Full Time!\", \"from\": 51, \"to\": 122, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This is the digital version of Full Time.\", \"from\": 124, \"to\": 165, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If you want it earlier, start every week with Full Time delivered to your inbox.Sign up here.\", \"from\": 166, \"to\": 259, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Those of us who stayed up last night were given a show of squad cohesion, offensive pressure and a long-range golazo.\", \"from\": 261, \"to\": 378, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The problem for USWNT fans is that they came from the Mexican national team instead of the U.S. Having likely studied film from USWNT's match against Argentina last week, Mexico came out with energy and pressure that the U.S. could not match andtopped Group A with a 2-0 winover the U.S.\", \"from\": 379, \"to\": 666, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 395, \"end\": 400, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"USWNT\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\"}, {\"begin\": 433, \"end\": 440, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mexico\", \"score\": 0.9994950701318317, \"rank\": 0.000505184368206797, \"text\": \"Mexican\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mexico\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mexico\"}, {\"begin\": 507, \"end\": 512, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"USWNT\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\"}, {\"begin\": 529, \"end\": 538, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9998161895323252, \"rank\": 0.00012753890968200348, \"text\": \"Argentina\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 550, \"end\": 556, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mexico_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999870415970835, \"rank\": 1.2949547905448788e-05, \"text\": \"Mexico\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mexico_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mexico_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 631, \"end\": 638, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Group_A\", \"score\": 0.9992398414638304, \"rank\": 0.0007607367597031051, \"text\": \"Group A\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Group_A\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Group_A\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Here's how it went down:  \\u00a1Un GO-LA-ZO de Pelayo sella el paso a los Cuartos de Final para M\\u00e9xico!\", \"from\": 667, \"to\": 765, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 709, \"end\": 715, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pelagius_of_Asturias\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.116340272244622e-14, \"text\": \"Pelayo\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pelagius_of_Asturias\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pelagius_of_Asturias\"}, {\"begin\": 722, \"end\": 729, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2019_El_Paso_shooting\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.5407432665333892e-15, \"text\": \"el paso\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2019_El_Paso_shooting\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2019_El_Paso_shooting\"}, {\"begin\": 758, \"end\": 764, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mexico_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999998564399096, \"rank\": 1.413793603276065e-07, \"text\": \"M\\u00e9xico\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mexico_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mexico_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\ud83d\\udca5pic.twitter.com/qy2C6vfseN  - W Gold Cup (@GoldCup)February 27, 2024    With two wins, one loss and a seven-goal differential, theUSWNT qualifies for the quarterfinals as second-place finishers in Group A, but points and goal differential matter as teams are re-seeded ahead of the next round.\", \"from\": 766, \"to\": 1060, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 965, \"end\": 972, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Group_A\", \"score\": 0.9992398414638304, \"rank\": 0.0007607367597031051, \"text\": \"Group A\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Group_A\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Group_A\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Advertisement  The final places for the quarterfinals will be decided on Tuesday when Colombia faces Puerto Rico and Brazil faces Panama, and also on Wednesday when Canada goes against Costa Rica and Paraguay takes on El Salvador.\", \"from\": 1062, \"to\": 1292, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1149, \"end\": 1157, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Colombia_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9985275840414658, \"rank\": 0.0014745772552401937, \"text\": \"Colombia\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Colombia_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/res